brainstorming with my friends,

289
00:15:17,800 --> 00:15:20,430
thinking, then creating something new...

290
00:15:20,730 --> 00:15:29,280
The Platinum Generation
"A convergence in the visual art department of Oonaka University of the Arts"
Kawagoe Kyoichi
N@NA
Akishima Shino

291
00:15:21,480 --> 00:15:24,880
